snippet.title: 🔋Cyborg 3003 - Gameplay Trailer - Play on Steam today!
snippet.description:
🔋You can play the game today on Steam, as an Early Access I will be able to improve the game with time based on your opinions. And my first question is: What you want to see next? new levels, new creatures or a new weapons?

Leave your comments here or on Steam. Thanks and let's have fun.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2516430/Cyborg3003/

Rodrigo Banzato.
